dcterms:description: The Monument dataset consists of pairs of English natural questions and intermediary SPARQL queries generated from 38 templates. It includes multiple versions generated using different combinations of KB elements.
dcterms:title: Monument

dcterms:creator: P. Trivedi
G. Maheshwari
M. Dubey
J. Lehmann
dcterms:description: The LC-QuAD dataset provides entries of multiple types (COUNT, ASK, SELECT) and covers a broad range of KB elements, with each entry containing an English natural language question and its corresponding SPARQL query generated from a template.
dcterms:title: LC-QuAD

dcterms:creator: X. Yin
D. Gromann
S. Rudolph
dcterms:description: The TNTSPA dataset is a version of the LC-QuAD dataset containing reformulated questions and queries found in the LC-QuADv1.0 dataset, but split differently for training and testing.
dcterms:title: TNTSPA

dcterms:creator: A. Hartmann
T. Soru
E. Marx
dcterms:description: The DBNQA dataset is composed of pairs of natural language questions and SPARQL queries, generated using a large number of question-query templates, and includes directly executable SPARQL queries.
dcterms:title: DBNQA
